Interface PCMElementMonitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, UniqueElement

    public interface PCMElementMonitor
extends UniqueElement
    A representation of the model object 'PCM Element Monitor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Measurement Specification
    • Pcm Element Classifier
